query:
SELECT 
                eq.id as queue_id,
                eq.document_id,
                sd.name,
                sd.content_type,
                sd.metadata
            FROM embedding_queue eq
            INNER JOIN source_documents sd ON sd.id = eq.document_id
            WHERE eq.status = 'pending' 
            AND eq.retry_count < 3
            ORDER BY eq.created_at ASC
            LIMIT $1
